  "url": "https://www.lankadeepa.lk/news/\u0d85\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca-\u0dbb\u0da7\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca-\u0db4\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1-\u0d9c\u0dd2\u0dba-\u0dad\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca-53\u0d9a\u0dca-\u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7/101-615935",
  "time_ut": 1657085654,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dc3\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0dbb\u0da7\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0d9c\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dad\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca 53\u0d9a\u0dca \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Another 53 were arrested for leaving the country without permission",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The navy said that 53 people were arrested from Trincomalee and Mannar along with two smugglers who were suspected of attempting to illegally migrate to a foreign country by sea.",
        "The group was arrested in Trincomalee Erakkandi and Mannar Talpadu coastal areas last night (5) and the suspects, aged between 1 and 52 years, were arrested in the operation conducted by the Sri Lanka Naval Ship Vijayaba under the Eastern Naval Command and Kuchchaveli Police. And the Navy said that they are residents of Kumburupiddy.",
        "The Navy said that 12 men, 11 women and 23 children were arrested during a special search operation conducted by the Sri Lanka Naval Ship Gajaba in Mannar, Talpadu beach area using a dinghy to try to migrate illegally to another country. The Navy also mentioned that two smugglers involved in the same smuggling along with 07 other people including 03 men and 03 children were taken into custody along with a dinghy at Talpadu beach.",
        "The Navy further stated that the suspects, aged between 05 and 48, were identified as residents of Colombo, Badulla, Vavnia and Mannarama and were handed over to the Mannar Police for further legal proceedings."
      ],
